OL,6,FBut Pitchfork applied for the decision
OL,7,Fto be reconsidered and this has been
OL,8,Fgranted, the Parole Board said on
OL,9,FMonday 12 Febrary.
OL,11,FIt means he will face another parole
OL,12,Fhearing to decide if he can be freed
OL,13,Ffrom jail.
OL,15,FIn a statement the Parole Board said:
OL,16,F"The decision refusing Mr Pitchfork's
OL,17,Frelease was eligible for
OL,18,Freconsideration under the Parole Board
OL,19,FRules.
