OL,3,CDouble child rapist and murderer Colin
OL,4,CPitchfork to face fresh parole hearing
OL,6,F"The reason the reconsideration
OL,7,Fapplication was granted was that the
OL,8,Foral hearing panel in 2023 had a duty
OL,9,Fto take the prison offender manager's
OL,10,Frecommendation into account and to
OL,11,Fgive adequate reasons for any
OL,12,Fdisagreement with that recommendation.
OL,13,FThe reconsideration member concluded
OL,14,Fthat the panel's reasoned decision did
OL,15,Fnot do so.
