OL,3,CDouble child rapist and murderer Colin
OL,4,CPitchfork to face fresh parole hearing
OL,6,F"The reconsideration member directed
OL,7,Fthat Mr Pitchfork's case must now be
OL,8,Freheard by a fresh panel of three
OL,9,FParole Board members. This panel will
OL,10,Fcomplete its own review of Mr
OL,11,FPitchfork's case, including hearing
OL,12,Foral evidence and will decide whether
OL,13,Fhe meets the legal test for release.
OL,14,FThe reconsideration member advised the
OL,15,Fnew panel that the fact that this is a
OL,16,Freconsideration should not in any way
OL,17,Faffect their decision. It is a
OL,18,Fcomplete re-hearing.
